  {
    "type": "EXEGETICAL (ORIGINAL LANGUAGES)",
    "name": "Meyer's NT Commentary",
    "elements": [
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "Matthew 11:13-14",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " are by way of showing how it happens that, ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "since the commencement of the Baptist’s ministry",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ", the Messiah’s kingdom has been the object toward which such a violent movement has been directed. All the prophets, and even the law, have prophesied ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "up till John’s time;",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " John was the ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "terminus ad quem",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " of the period of prophecy which he brought to a close, and he who forms the termination of this epoch then steps upon the scene as the immediate forerunner of the Messiah—as the ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "Elias",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " who was to come. Accordingly, that new violent stirring of life among the people must be connected with this manifestation of Elias. Others interpret differently, while Bleek and Holtzmann are even inclined to suppose that originally ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "Matthew 11:13",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " was uttered ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "before",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "Matthew 11:12",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ".",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "p",
        "text": "",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "br",
            "class": "",
            "text": "",
